<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢١٢٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/118">إِبْرَاهِيمُ بْنُ مُوسَى: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6833">الْوَلِيدُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1081">ثَوْرٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1759">خَالِدِ بْنِ مَعْدَانَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6328">الْمِقْدَامِ بْنِ مَعْدِيْكَرِبَ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«كِيلُوا طَعَامَكُمْ يُبَارَكْ لَكُمْ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>